88
00:06:28,922 --> 00:06:30,921
Dan dijatuhi hukuman di Fort Rozz.

89
00:06:30,922 --> 00:06:34,761
Sama seperti Krypton, planet ini
di ambang kehancuran ekologi.

90
00:06:34,762 --> 00:06:36,602
